    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minimal signs of wear on the upholstery. While the exterior paint still shines, you may find a few small door dings or light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Overall, it is a reliable and presentable car that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
