      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It looks and feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
