      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been comprehensively serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner plates to ensure structural rigidity. The factory M-Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional power delivery out of corners. The exterior retains its original luster with zero paint correction required, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A collector-tier example with a fully documented service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
