    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating recently applied, showing absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in untouched condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history fully documented from the original delivery date. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the smallest ambient interior light, functions exactly as intended. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history of fair-weather driving only. Brand new performance tires were recently installed, and the vehicle has passed a rigorous multi-point inspection with zero recommendations for repair. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands absolute perfection.",
